# Eliminar Pantallas Secundarias

El objetivo es simplificar la interfaz dejando únicamente el "Centro de Control" (Dashboard),# Removing Flashcards From Nueva Intervencion

The user wants to simplify the "Nueva Intervencion" screen by removing the checklist flashcards, while keeping the rest of the layout and navigation intact.

## Proposed Changes

### `ultmo ignealis.html`
- **[MODIFY] [ultmo ignealis.html](file:///c:/Users/Gustavo/Desktop/Pruebas/ultmo%20ignealis.html)**: 
  - Remove the small "✓ Dirección", "✓ Tipo" flashcards from beneath the transcription block.
  - Fix the main CSS stylesheet to strictly hide `display: none !important;` `.screen` elements when they don't have the `.active` class, preventing screens from stacking over each other.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Verify that clicking "Nueva Intervencion" in the sidebar renders its content.
- Verify that clicking other items switches the screen completely without overlapping data.
- Comprobar la consola del navegador (`F12`) para asegurar que el Javascript no tire errores por elementos no encontrados (ej. animaciones referenciando elementos borrados).
